headline: Charles River Laboratories (CRL) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of lab services company Charles River Laboratories (NYSE:CRL) jumped 6.1% in the afternoon session after the company provided an encouraging business update at an investor conference, highlighting positive demand trends.
